<subSubSection id="91E06561FFC30D24FF5AF2D0FB87F2A9" pageId="4" pageNumber="459" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="D94536EAFFC30D24FF5AF2D0FB87F2A9" blockId="4.[138,1344,2546,3485]" pageId="4" pageNumber="459">
<emphasis id="EB8EEAF8FFC30D24FF5AF2D0FE58F291" bold="true" box="[141,495,3372,3405]" pageId="4" pageNumber="459">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. There has been no research on the Orange 
<taxonomicName id="1EFA4D69FFC30D24FE10F2A8FD9FF2A9" box="[455,552,3412,3445]" class="Mammalia" family="Cuniculidae" genus="Agouti" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="4" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Agouti</taxonomicName>
, at least under the name 
<taxonomicName id="1EFA4D69FFC30D24FC5AF2A8FB9BF2A9" authorityName="Wagler" authorityYear="1831" box="[909,1068,3412,3445]" class="Mammalia" family="Dasyproctidae" genus="Dasyprocta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="4" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="croconota">D. croconota</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
